                <div id="main-text">
                    
                    <p class="swing"><span contenteditable="true">1. Mekuru, Shiori meet Alexa</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Wow. I didn't know you'd write such cute, dumb things!</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">I was six.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">You were so cute as a kid!</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">She was, wasn't she?</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Click to Edit</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Click to Edit</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="rest1"><span contenteditable="true">She flips open to my diary.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="swing"><span contenteditable="true">2. Alexa shows she's an assistant. Tells them date and time.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">"But what is probably more important is this." Alexa flips to date and time.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Shiori looks at the date. She looks like she wants to throw up. "That's... This is a week before the murders."</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Click to Edit</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">"Destiny is inescapable," Alexa shrugs. She pats the book meaningfully against her palm... before dropping it on her foot. "AUGH!"<br>Seriously?<br><br></span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="swing"><span contenteditable="true">3. Monika comes barging in.&nbsp; With Alphonse.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Anybody home? Miss Monika here just insisted. // I hate to bring along anyone this angry around children, but...</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Shiori freezes when she sees Monika.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Alphonse decides to interject.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Why if it isn't lil Shiori! //What's the name of your friend Shiori? //His name's Yorick!</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">He looks like a happy fella, just like you, Shiori.&nbsp; //Mmmhmm.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">And hello, the little vicereine M herself. I've got to talk to your mother later. (as if he's responding to the simulation)</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true"><i>Alphonse Krabb./&nbsp;</i>Um. Hello Mr. Krabb. // Always so polite.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Now, Shiori, last time you hung around me and Ms. Crecer's place, you left a pamphlet.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">The Codex starts rustling. Shiori and I look at each other.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">The pamphlet starts shedding off lacquer and color like it's... molting.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Insert Shiori 1 here.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Neither Monika or Alphonse seem to respond at all. They're arguing.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">"I was just playing here, Monika..."</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">That's when Monika walks over to grab Shiori's hand.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">"Hey!"</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">But it's Alphonse who steps in.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">"Yeah, well everyone's talking shit about me because they say I don't know where you are. You're coming home."</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true"></span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">And what does she do at home? Alphonse growled. She sits alone. I'd say she's in better company here.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">If you bring this girl home, are you going to watch her? Spend time with her?&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true"></span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">She's <i>twelve </i>you sanctimonious prick. This is the safest place in the universe. So safe it's <i>boring.&nbsp;</i></span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">They go running around the entire town, and no one stops them, but I'm the bad guy for keeping her in a house?&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
                    <p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">If you won't take care of this child, you might as well leave her here until you learn to be a proper adult.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Yeah? Tell the sheriff about it.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat2"><span contenteditable="true">Touch her and I will, Alphonse growled.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
                    <p class="beat1"><span contenteditable="true">Shiori dabbed at her eyes a bit.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="beat1"><span contenteditable="true">Mr. Krabb she'll just get me later anyway.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
                    <p class="beat3"><span contenteditable="true">Click here to edit</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="swing"><span contenteditable="true">4. The seance. Which takes place in the courthouse.</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="admonition"><span contenteditable="true">Utilize the s√©ance to emphasize how the town was suspicious of Shiori.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="admonition"><span contenteditable="true">Establish that Shiori and Mekuru get slightly pulled into their former selves.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="admonition"><span contenteditable="true">Creepy things in seance like... I'm not sure.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p><p class="swing"><span contenteditable="true">?. At some point, Alexa comes in to shut things down.&nbsp;</span><button class="add-button"><img src="./images/add.png"></button><button class="minus-button"><img src="./images/MINUS.png"></button></p>
